         <h3>Business Intelligence</h3>
         <p class="text-style-1 offset-top-22">
          In today's competitive business environment, effective Business Intelligence(BI) enables companies to quickly identify,
          respond, and adapt to emerging trends and new opportunities. Effective BI reaches all corners of the organization,
          enabling all decision-makers to drive increased business performance at strategic, tactical, and organizational levels.
          <br />
          <br />
          As the business process today is more dynamic than ever, with mergers and acquisitions, consolidation and regulatory
          changes. The Main challenges faced by Clients Are:
          <br />
          Growing volumes of organizational data and the ability to leverage it effectively in less time and with more certainty.
          <br />
          Absence of consistent master data, enterprise information and systems to manage the same.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="cell-xs-12 offset-top-38 offset-sm-top-0">
        <h3 class="offset-top-15"></h3>
        <div class="inset-sm-left-30">
         <p class="offset-top-15">
          <b>These in turn lead to the following:</b>
         </p>
         <ul class="list-marked list-marked-spacing-lg offset-top-22">
          <li>Ineffective business process/performance/predictability management.</li>
          <li>Inefficient utilization of technology models/architectures and coupling.</li>
          <li>Lack of optimization in resource utilization.</li>
          <li>Uncertainty and hence, degradation in the quality of service.</li>
          <li>Non-compliance issues.</li>
         </ul>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="cell-xs-12">
        <div class="inset-md-right-15 shift-up-sm-10">
         <h4>
          <br />
         </h4>
         <p class="text-style-1 offset-top-22">
          Hence to overcome these challenges and to succeed, an enterprise needs to develop an ability to sense these changes, and
          thus respond to them quickly and smartly. Our Business Intelligence and Performance Management solution helps your
          enterprise in fulfilling the aspirations of being agile, adaptable and efficient.
          <br />
          <br />
          Arka Technologies Inc BI solutions help enterprise customers deal with a critical business problem: the need for a
          real-time view of overall company operations. An integrated view of company operations leads to faster, better decision
          making by executives, managers, and information workers throughout an organization on a day-to-day basis.
          <br />
          <br />
          Getting that overall, integrated view, however, is often quite challenging because companies frequently need to access
          data from multiple, disparate line-of-business systems, including those of third-party software vendors and ERP systems,
          such as SAP, and Siebel.
          <br />
          <br />
          We help our customers to define and design a BI strategy that fits the unique requirements of their organization and
          provides a complete, integrated view of their overall organizational health. Arka Technologies Inc implements BI
          solutions across all verticals, with a focus on financial services, healthcare, and communication etc.
          <br />
          <br />
          Also When you add new or update existing products, or migrate software from a legacy system, you need to start off with
          the momentum that delivers immediate value. Our Implementation Services help you accelerate the implementation of your
          solution so that you can rapidly achieve the business benefits you expect.
          <br />
          <br />
          We utilize a proven, structured approach to implement your solution – all supported by strong project management and
          flexible education and change management offerings to help your project team work toward success. Best of all, our
          implementation services are scalable, customizable, and can be delivered at your site.
          <br />
          <br />
          Arka Technologies Inc's Implementation Services cover all phases of your solution implementation from planning to
          deployment and support.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="cell-xs-12 offset-top-38 offset-sm-top-0">
        <h3 class="offset-top-15"></h3>
        <div class="inset-sm-left-30">
         <p class="offset-top-15"></p>
         <ul class="list-marked list-marked-spacing-lg offset-top-22">
          <li><b>Plan</b>: Prepare for implementation, establish project success criteria, and plan the project scope
           including schedule, risk mitigation, communications, and overall project guidelines.</li>
          <li><b>Assess</b>: Collaborate with all of your diverse organizations to understand their needs, and then work with
           your core project team to design a consolidated solution to maximize employee efficiency, application performance, and
           overall business benefits.</li>
          <li><b>Learning and Discovery</b>: Use a combination of formal knowledge transfer and collaborative workshops to
           educate your project team, understand your business requirements, and share best practices.</li>
          <li><b>Solution Build</b>: Build your solution according to your documented business requirement, including
           installing and configuring the application, managing data migration, designing and implementing connectivity,
           customizing required product extensions, and performing unit testing to verify the solution build.</li>
          <li><b>Test and Certify</b>: Support your system and integration testing, resolve all critical open issues,
           initiate end user training, and plan for system deployment.</li>
          <li><b>Deploy and Support</b>: Assist your transition from a project-oriented, pre-production environment to a
           successful and live production operation reinforced by our Global Support.</li>
         </ul>
        </div>
